# TODO:

Install docker
Install docker-compose

if permission issues persist, set env var UID and GID with the user who should own the filesystem


to start:
docker-compose up -d app

to restart:
docker-compose down; docker-compose up -d app



To override default ports for frontend:

PORT_APP = default 8080
PORT_PMA = default 8081
PORT_MAIL = default 8082


PORT_APP=8082 PORT_PMA=8083 docker-compose up -d app
